unittitle_ssm: Communications Workers of America, District 4 Records
abstract_ssm: Communications Workers of America, District 4 represents workers in telecommunications, informational technology, publishing, print and electronic media, manufacturing, higher education, local government and health care in Illinois, Indiana, Ohio, Michigan and Wisconsin. The collection contains bargaining materials, correspondence, and convention proceedings.
